/*.snapshot.md

# What IS copied in stage 1 (Tailwind build):
#   package.json, tailwind.config.js, src/, es/, en/
# What IS copied in stage 2 (nginx serve):
#   index.html, 404.html, 404-en.html, sitemap.xml, robots.txt, boats.js
#   es/, en/, assets/, nginx.conf, src/styles/main.css
